{"id":504,"parent_id":0,"book_id":8,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":504,"title":"Firstfruits","subtitle":"","short_title":"Firstfruits","uri":"/scriptures/bd/firstfruits","content":[["div",{"id":"t1","uri":"/scriptures/bd/firstfruits.t1","order":".000.1314"},[".title","Firstfruits"],["div",{"id":"p1","uri":"/scriptures/bd/firstfruits.p1","order":".000.1315"},"Regarded as belonging to God, and offered by the nation as a whole at the great feasts, and by private individuals at other times (",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.29"},"Ex. 22:29"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/23.19"},"23:19"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/34.26"},"34:26"],"). The prescribed ritual included (1) the waving before the Lord of a sheaf of barley on the morrow of the Passover Sabbath (",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/23.10-14"},"Lev. 23:10–14"],"); (2) the offering of two loaves made with new wheat flour at the Feast of Pentecost (",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/34.22"},"Ex. 34:22"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/23.15,17"},"Lev. 23:15, 17"],"); (3) a thanksgiving for the harvest at the Feast of Tabernacles, or of Ingathering (",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/23.16"},"Ex. 23:16"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/34.22"},"34:22"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/23.39"},"Lev. 23:39"],"). See also",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/num/15.19,21"},"Num. 15:19, 21"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/26.2-11"},"Deut. 26:2–11"],". Rules with regard to private offerings of firstfruits are found in",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/23.16"},"Ex. 23:16"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/2.12-16"},"Lev. 2:12–16"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/19.23-25"},"19:23–25"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/22.14"},"22:14"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/23.15-17"},"23:15–17"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/num/15.19-21"},"Num. 15:19–21"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/18.4"},"Deut. 18:4"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/26.2"},"26:2"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-chr/31.5,11"},"2 Chr. 31:5, 11"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/neh/10.35,37"},"Neh. 10:35, 37"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/neh/12.44"},"12:44"],"."]]],"refs":null}
